DarkMouse::

She was brave, but even brave rodents felt nervous, which was what 
she was feeling. She couldn't help but rack her circuits for her 
memory on this bot. She watched as the scenery past by in a  
blurr. "UH, so where is this base pray tell?"  looking up at him as 
he carried her through the sky. She felt something in her spark jump. 
Why did her instincts start screaming that something was wrong, but 
she coudln't put her finger on it.
